latestIgtvVideos.title: Belly Dance Workshop 😍 My first
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Had the pleasure and the honour of attending a belly dance workshop by my guru @mohnaa.shrivastava and I couldn’t be happier! We spent an hour and a half or so on this piece toh Kaafi jagah bhul gayi Mai 😂😂

But that is nothing in comparison to the joy I felt while doing this. Took my little sister too (chup gayi mere peeche Wo😂🙈) but @mohnaa.shrivastava YOURE the best teacher I’ve ever had and one of the most amazing human beings I’ve ever met. 

I already have told you how much joy you bring in my life and I can’t wait to dance more with you!! Asap❤️❤️

Thank you for this experience, it’s the first of many for me❤️💋

If you guys are looking to learn then she is your person! Hit her up and how her some loveeeeee❤️

latestPosts.caption:
Your girl is on the @forbesindia Top 100 Digital Stars list !! ( at no 87 😋😋) !!!! 🥺🥺🥺🥺🥺🥺

This year has been a mental whirlwind for me but just as it is coming to an end, I was given this good news!  It’s been really hard to keep my head straight but I try my best to bring genuine, informative, and entertaining content your way. 

There were many many hard decisions to take while trying to maintain my sanity after the Tik Tok wave but I guess staying true to yourself does pay off and to be recognized by the amazing folks at Forbes was something I never even thought of. 

There’s so so many of my creator friends on this list which makes my heart happy and I also feel proud to have made it on here with the small community we’ve built here. ❤️

It was already crazy to have been considered for the list but to actually make it on it is still sinking in. We have so many amazing creators with crazy influence in India so this feels very very special. 

Thank you. I love you. This is huge for me and I’m still wrapping my head around this. 🥺❤️

Baaki, all my love to my team and my babies @dancewithshristy @thepicturephacctory @tanvi._.thakkar ❤️❤️❤️ onwards and upwards from here! 

#lilmissgurung #Forbes100DigitalStars

I’m trying to be a physically fit person (eventually) and I was feeling particularly energetic today so I thought I’d check to see if I remember anything from my childhood gymnastic days 😂😂 

Turns out my muscles do remember the handstand(with a slight run up😂) and the cartwheels (will take a video to motivate self) but they also remember the crap I’ve been eating for the last 5 years 😂😂😂😂😂

#handtstand

A whole year to this video! ❤️❤️ 
I posted my 30 days of Saree series around this time last year and it was the most fun I had in a long time. Haven’t had the mental capacity to shoot or post anything fresh but this old video reminded me of a happy and fulfilling time so I thought I’d share it with you to bring some joy❤️
